Bereaved families of childcare accidents (right) to press a press conference on the results of the "Family Support Center Project" = 27 pm
On the 27th, a private survey found that 35% of municipalities in Ichi Ward and Machi-mura implemented their own safety measures for "Family Support Center Project" (famispo), which connects parents who want to temporarily leave their children and support members who are entrusted to them at private homes.
