Ice observed for the first time this season at Tsuruke Pond in Mt. Norikura Tajodaira = 27, Tanyukawa-cho, Takayama City (provided by Norikura Skyline Management Office)
On the 27th, ice was observed for the first time this season at Tsuruke Pond in Tajodaira (Tanyukawa-cho, Takayama City, Gifu Prefecture, elevation 2702 meters).
